      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me and is still in great shape for its next adventure! It runs smoothly and has been really well-taken care of\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 32500.0,
