    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential driver's tool powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a broad torque curve thanks to the double-VANOS system. The power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the chassis handles high lateral G-loads with confidence. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with an honest 'good' condition driver, the suspension geometry remains true and the steering rack is remarkably communicative. A purist-spec example ready for spirited B-road duty.",
